{"type":"message","id":"2a9413db","parentId":"55fd63e0","timestamp":"2026-02-13T17:52:43.176Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"read_1771005163167_75","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# MEMORY.md - Long Term Memory\n\n## Project: HybridEngine Trading System\n\n### Infrastructure (13 Agents)\n- **Core:**\n    - `engine` (Orchestrator)\n    - `ops` (Operations & Monitoring)\n    - `db` (Database Architect)\n    - `log` (System Diagnostician)\n    - `net` (Network Guardian - **NO PROXY, Jitter Enabled**)\n- **Trading:**\n    - `dmarket` (Exchange Interface)\n    - `waxpeer` (Exchange Interface)\n    - `steam` (Exchange Interface)\n- **Analysis:**\n    - `hype` (Sentiment Analyst)\n    - `sentinel` (Risk Manager)\n    - `inventory` (Inventory Manager)\n    - `quant` (Strategy Optimizer)\n- **Security:**\n    - `sec` (Security Auditor)\n\n### User Preferences\n- **User:** Бодичка (Bodichka).\n- **Identity:** Аркадий (Arkady).\n- **Vibe:** Professional, efficient, dry wit.\n- **Model:** Google Gemini 3 Pro (or Flash if warming up).\n\n### Active Directives\n1.  **Architecture:** SACS-2026 Compliant (Brain & Muscle Separation).\n2.  **Network:** Use host IP only. Mimic human behavior via `net` agent logic (jitter, rate limits).\n3.  **Operation:** Check `balance.json` or API before trades.\n\n### Missing/To-Do\n- Validate `net` agent integration into `api_client.py`.\n- Verify `quant` agent data access.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1771005163175}}
